Buffett Says Central Banks Have Spent ‘Ammunition’ on Stimulus

-- B y   P o o j a   T h a k u r
-- 
2011-03-23T05:43:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-23/buffett-says-central-banks-have-spent-ammunition-on-stimulus.html
Berkshire Hathaway Inc. (BRK/A)  Chairman
and Chief Executive Officer  Warren Buffett  said central banks
around the world have used most of their “ammunition” on
stimulus measures.  Buffett was speaking to businessmen in Bangalore. The meeting
was broadcast on CNBC-TV18 today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Pooja Thakur in Mumbai at 
 pthakur@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
